  "system": {
    "itemKey": "",
    "description": "<p>You conjure a protective elemental ward in response to damage.</p><p><strong>Trigger:</strong> When you take Elemental Damage.</p><p><strong>Reaction:</strong> Make a DC 15 Spell Check.</p><ul><li><p><strong>Failure:</strong> You gain Resistance (1) to the triggering damage type until the end of the turn, this also applies to the triggering damage.</p></li><li><p><strong>Success:</strong> Resistance (2).</p></li><li><p><strong>Success (10):</strong> Resistance (3).</p></li></ul><p></p><p><span style=\"text-decoration: underline;\"><strong><span style=\"text-decoration: underline;\">Spell Enhancements</span></strong></span></p><p><strong>Amplified Shield: (1 AP, Repeatable)</strong> The Resistance increases by 1.</p><p><strong>Flow of Nature: (1 MP, Repeatable)</strong> You deal +2 damage of the triggering damage type on your next Attack made until the end of your next turn.</p><p><strong>Lingering Retaliation: (X MP)</strong> For the next minute, when a creature Hits you with a Melee Attack, it takes X damage of the triggering damage type.</p>",
